latest update:

Adds:
  - [data manager] added a second user authentication system for connecting your users to your app.
Changes:
  - [data manager] added a reload configuration button instead of reloading it at every changes.
  - [bundle editor] optimized the ReactJS build by reducing its size by 50%.
BugFixes:
  - [bundle editor] now properly extract the CSS for VueJS bundles.
  - [bundle editor] the building messages are now displayed near the build spinner.
  - [bundle editor] now disable the build spinner if an error occurs.
Troubleshooting:
  - If you have a problem seeing your files after the update delete the admins collection in mongodb and restart the app, this will create an updated superuser with all the new authorizations.
